get.description:
Get a bot by URL identifier (slug).

Restricted bots are 404-invisible to actors without use access;
org owners and platform admins see them with ``can_use=false``.

ConversationSecurityRedactionEvent.description:
Best-effort live UX event for a user-message ingress redaction.

Reload rendering uses the persisted ``TextContent.metadata`` on the message;
this event is just the immediate Centrifugo path.
